Package: GCVieweR
Type: Package
Title: Gene Cluster Visualizations in R
Version: 0.1.3
Author: Niels van der Velden
Maintainer: Niels van der Velden <n.s.j.vandervelden@gmail.com>
Description: 'GCVieweR' is an R package designed to plot gene arrow maps. 
             It allows side by side visualization of multiple gene clusters and 
             has options to add a legend, labels, annotations, customized scales, 
             colors, tooltips and much more.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.0
URL: https://github.com/nvelden/GCVieweR
BugReports: https://github.com/nvelden/GCVieweR/issues
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5.0),
    dplyr,
    rlang
Imports:
    htmlwidgets,
    magrittr
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    shiny,
    biomaRt
VignetteBuilder: knitr
